The paper deals with the parameterization of MaxSat, which is a well-known problem in the area of computational complexity and optimization. The paper also discusses the Hitting Set problem, which is a classic problem in computer science and has applications in various fields. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics).
